title: Bridget Phetasy
itunes:title: Bridget Phetasy
description:
Comedian Bridget Phetasy comes on the pod this week and tells Whitney about almost being on the REAL WORLD, the eternal meh, and the amazing snacks at Marijuana Anonymous meetings.  We also hear about how she made up her own last name.  Check out Bridget's podcasts DUMPSTER FIRE and WALK-INS WELCOME wherever you get your pods.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
